125
00:20:49,657 --> 00:20:53,721
Elle-même, itself, the self.

126
00:20:53,761 --> 00:20:54,883
No, no, no, no.

127
00:20:54,903 --> 00:20:56,585
The emotion itself can't be a self.

128
